-- title

Determine Span Types Directly Inside Span Files

-- h2

Overview

This feature adds a `{# type: #}`` comment to the
start of every theme span file. The three possible
values are:

-- list

- `{# type: standard #}``

- `{# type: key-value #}``

- `{# type: internal #}``

-- p

The "standard" and "key-value" spans become
available as span tags while the internal
ones are used only by other templates directly




